trans-unit.source: Represents the license transform algorithm used to normalize XrML licenses for signatures.
trans-unit.target: Representa o algoritmo de transformação de licença usado para normalizar licenças XrML para assinaturas.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.XmlLicenseTransform> class represents the license transform algorithm as defined in the MPEG Rights Extension Language (MPEG REL).
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.XmlLicenseTransform> classe representa o algoritmo de transformação de licença, conforme definido na linguagem da extensão de direitos MPEG (MPEG REL).

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.XmlLicenseTransform> class to transform XrML licenses for signatures.
trans-unit.target: Use o <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.XmlLicenseTransform> classe XrML licenças para assinaturas de transformação.

trans-unit.source: The Uniform Resource Identifier (URI) that describes the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.XmlLicenseTransform> class is defined by the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedXml.XmlLicenseTransformUrl> field.
trans-unit.target: O URI Uniform Resource Identifier () que descreve o <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.XmlLicenseTransform> classe é definida pelo <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedXml.XmlLicenseTransformUrl> campo.

trans-unit.source: The following code example shows how to validate an XML digital signature using the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.IRelDecryptor> interface and the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.XmlLicenseTransform> class.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo de código a seguir mostra como validar uma assinatura digital XML usando o <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.IRelDecryptor> interface e o <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.XmlLicenseTransform> classe.

trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.XmlLicenseTransform" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the decryptor of the current <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.XmlLicenseTransform" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o descriptografador do objeto <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.XmlLicenseTransform" /> atual.

trans-unit.source: The decryptor of the current <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.XmlLicenseTransform" /> object.
trans-unit.target: O descriptografador do atual <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.XmlLicenseTransform" /> objeto.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.XmlLicenseTransform> object uses an <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.IRelDecryptor> interface to decrypt `<encryptedGrant>` elements from the current `<license>` element.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.XmlLicenseTransform> objeto usa um <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.IRelDecryptor> interface descriptografar `<encryptedGrant>` elementos da atual `<license>` elemento.

trans-unit.target: O exemplo de código a seguir mostra como validar uma assinatura digital XML usando o <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.IRelDecryptor> interface e o <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.XmlLicenseTransform> classe.
